 ication window 14-21 July 2026. ELIGIBILITY: US non-profits with 501(c)(3)
  status\, units of state or local government\, or federally-recognised tri
 bal communities\; organisations must have a three-year history of programm
 ing and meet a minimum operating budget. Project grants typically USD 10\,
 000 to USD 100\,000+\, with most awards in the USD 10\,000-50\,000 range\;
  a 1:1 cost-share is required. Natural sibling to the NEH Public Humanitie
 s Projects programme on the desk.\n\nOrganisation: National Endowment for 
