DESCRIPTION:Open call for the 5th edition of Peckham Digital\, a festival c
 elebrating creative computing. This call is for the PROGRAMME track: artis
 ts\, creative technologists and creative coders to facilitate workshops\, 
 present talks\, provide demos\, or deliver performances (the separate Artw
 ork Open Call covers exhibition pieces). Emerging applicants explicitly we
 lcomed\; over half of past Peckham Digital artists had this as their first
