 th skills in digital illustration and light animation\, supporting Third W
 ave Fund's gender-justice and liberation visibility\, fundraising and dono
 r mobilisation. Deliverables in 2026: two digital illustrations and one sh
 ort-form animated reel for storytelling and fundraising. Five-month reside
